  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definitions\n\n1.1\n\nUnless otherwise stated, this Part applies to:\n\n  1. (1) the _FSCS_ ;\n  2. (2) a _firm_ ; and\n  3. (3) [Deleted]\n  4. (4) the _Society_.\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*\n\n1.2\n\nIn this Part, the following definitions shall apply:\n\n_MERS levy_\n\nmeans a levy imposed by the _FSCS_ on a _firm_ or, where applicable, the _Society_ , to meet _relevant expenses_ incurred by the _FSCS_ in connection with acting on behalf of the _manager of the relevant scheme_ in accordance with Part 15A of _FSMA_.\n\n_manager of the relevant scheme_\n\nhas the meaning given in section 224B(3) of _FSMA_.\n\n_relevant expenses_\n\nmeans management expenses as defined in section 224F(7) of _FSMA_.\n\n_relevant scheme_\n\nmeans a scheme or arrangement (other than the _Financial Services Compensation Scheme_) for the payment of compensation (in certain cases) to customers (including customers outside the _United Kingdom_) in respect of _deposits_ or under contracts of insurance or in respect of similar financial services.\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*\n\n2\n\n###  Management Expenses in Respect of Relevant Schemes Levy\n\n2.1\n\nThis Chapter applies only to the _FSCS_.\n\n*Effective: 03/07/2015*\n\n2.2\n\nThe _FSCS_ may at any time impose a _MERS levy_ on a _firm_ or, where applicable, the _Society_ provided that the _FSCS_ has reasonable grounds for believing that the funds available to it to meet _relevant expenses_ are, or will be insufficient, taking into account _relevant expenses_ already incurred or expected to be incurred in the 12 _months_ immediately following the date of the levy.\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*\n\n2.3\n\nThe _FSCS_ can impose a _MERS levy_ only if the _FSCS_ has tried its best and has failed to obtain reimbursement of those expenses from the _manager of the relevant scheme_.\n\n*Effective: 03/07/2015*\n\n2.4\n\nThe _FSCS_ must calculate a share of a _MERS levy_ for a _firm_ or, where applicable, the _Society_ , on a reasonable basis.\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*\n\n3\n\n###  Obligation to Pay\n\n3.1\n\nA _firm_ (and, where applicable, the _Society_) must pay to the _FSCS_ its share of each _MERS levy_.\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*\n\n4\n\n###  Payments\n\n4.1\n\nA _firm_ (and, where applicable, the _Society_) must pay its share of a _MERS levy_ in one payment.\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*\n\n4.2\n\nA share of a _MERS levy_ is due on, and payable within, 30 days of the date when the invoice is issued.\n\n*Effective: 12/10/2016*\n\n4.3\n\nA _firm_ (and, where applicable, the _Society_) must pay its share of a _MERS levy_ by either direct debit, credit transfer (e.g. BACS or CHAPS), cheque, Maestro, Visa Debit or by credit card (Visa/Mastercard/American Express only).\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*\n\n4.4\n\nThe _FSCS_ may reduce, remit or refund any overpaid amounts paid in respect of a _MERS levy_ in respect of a particular period, due to a mistake of law or fact by a _firm_ or, where applicable, the _Society_ , provided that the claim is made by the _firm_ or, where applicable, the _Society_ not more than two years after the beginning of the period to which the overpayment relates.\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*\n\n4.5\n\nIf a _firm_ (and, where applicable, the _Society_), does not pay the total amount of its share of a _MERS levy_ , before the end of the date on which it is due, it must pay an additional amount as follows:\n\n  1. (1) if the _MERS levy_ was not paid in full before the end of the due date, an administrative fee of £250; and\n  2. (2) interest on any unpaid part of the _MERS levy_ or administrative fee at the rate of 5% per annum above the Official Bank Rate from time to time in force, accruing on a daily basis from the date on which the amount concerned became due.\n\n*Effective: 30/11/2022*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"0655b369a016410ea058023fdff7028e\" id=\"71aa7030525f40158d4e89b51f5ae1b1\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definitions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"c3c6f9a0882347ecb69a1b0910105d14\" id=\"70572e37e7c24128b9e783f46a2b045a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Unless otherwise stated, this Part applies to:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(2) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>; and</li>\n<li>(3) [Deleted]</li>\n<li>(4) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/03-07-2015#70572e37e7c24128b9e783f46a2b045a\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.1 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"6639e8a528b743fcbb3dab3986364c2c\" id=\"d8e0ae055c7b4b718431aceb955412a0\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>In this Part, the following definitions shall apply:</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means a levy imposed by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> on a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> or, where applicable, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>, to meet <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53193\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-5ea541b518a74229a5591d47a49af75c\" title=\"relevant expenses\">relevant expenses</a></em> incurred by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> in connection with acting on behalf of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53191\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-31ed4954f85a4b10b70c654d46b454ce\" title=\"manager of the relevant scheme\">manager of the relevant scheme</a></em> in accordance with Part 15A of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em>.</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53191\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-31ed4954f85a4b10b70c654d46b454ce\" title=\"manager of the relevant scheme\">manager of the relevant scheme</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">has the meaning given in section 224B(3) of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em>.</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53193\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-5ea541b518a74229a5591d47a49af75c\" title=\"relevant expenses\">relevant expenses</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means management expenses as defined in section 224F(7) of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em>.</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53194\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-60a7bae846504ff5bc311348b5cb3288\" title=\"relevant scheme\">relevant scheme</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means a scheme or arrangement (other than the <em class=\"rule-style-2\">Financial Services Compensation Scheme</em>) for the payment of compensation (in certain cases) to customers (including customers outside the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52722\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-e7e8282fcb5845be90310e2bc45fc55b\" title=\"United Kingdom\">United Kingdom</a></em>) in respect of <em class=\"rule-style-2\">deposits</em> or under contracts of insurance or in respect of similar financial services.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/03-08-2015#d8e0ae055c7b4b718431aceb955412a0\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.2 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"4439f74879e643fc9c6a53bfad3e6471\" id=\"99c100681b0747e2ae0b33220b7f336e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tManagement Expenses in Respect of Relevant Schemes Levy\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"bb3b2363254847d1856e3a990b32d2b8\" id=\"a82c080561bc4f8b96b47d203fc4690a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Chapter applies only to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/07/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"b6a4a9032d3345c684cffffd2c8bae28\" id=\"4be14e420c554f8596f926492fc23373\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> may at any time impose a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> on a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> or, where applicable, the<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em> provided that the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> has reasonable grounds for believing that the funds available to it to meet <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53193\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-5ea541b518a74229a5591d47a49af75c\" title=\"relevant expenses\">relevant expenses</a></em> are, or will be insufficient, taking into account <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53193\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-5ea541b518a74229a5591d47a49af75c\" title=\"relevant expenses\">relevant expenses</a></em> already incurred or expected to be incurred in the 12 <em class=\"rule-style-2\">months</em> immediately following the date of the levy.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/03-07-2015#4be14e420c554f8596f926492fc23373\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 2.2 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"65de9229864c428cae0c7507e18db047\" id=\"e3a9aff812054a46afad6b811f5d9a66\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> can impose a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> only if the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> has tried its best and has failed to obtain reimbursement of those expenses from the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53191\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-31ed4954f85a4b10b70c654d46b454ce\" title=\"manager of the relevant scheme\">manager of the relevant scheme</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/07/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"911531407a694859985fa01da69e0c87\" id=\"65eaa9e3ff8746e1917da889879e6951\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> must calculate a share of a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> for a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> or, where applicable, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>, on a reasonable basis.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/03-07-2015#65eaa9e3ff8746e1917da889879e6951\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 2.4 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"249f2ec408794fbcbe36f2ad380ee7fb\" id=\"9d87acd661d44422b981158742022b30\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tObligation to Pay\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"0adf99299f5f4e8092210e4abca1bd8e\" id=\"2759c5312d9a431290538f723c864f20\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> (and, where applicable, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>) must pay to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> its share of each <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/03-07-2015#2759c5312d9a431290538f723c864f20\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.1 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"6aad9799ddfb49519c327fa86ba584ed\" id=\"24ef60f9aa8d4b918b3800b8fbee8c57\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t4\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tPayments\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"e4c70308199e4bf686336ac454d51409\" id=\"08f23c07040b45fdbdc406a4e3621a58\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> (and, where applicable, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>) must pay its share of a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> in one payment.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/12-10-2016#08f23c07040b45fdbdc406a4e3621a58\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.1 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"3944eab093b44b9992b8c51e36380857\" id=\"5d131e96645e4c42b278a14b22ddc578\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A share of a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> is due on, and payable within, 30 days of the date when the invoice is issued.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t12/10/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/03-07-2015#5d131e96645e4c42b278a14b22ddc578\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.2 before 12/10/2016\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"97b8ccda8e93482d98359a2d883299a3\" id=\"91b1a3ea43bc4ac68bc49697f2c6c757\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> (and, where applicable, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>) must pay its share of a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> by either direct debit, credit transfer (e.g. BACS or CHAPS), cheque, Maestro, Visa Debit or by credit card (Visa/Mastercard/American Express only).</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/12-10-2016#91b1a3ea43bc4ac68bc49697f2c6c757\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.3 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"8629e1d872c449a087a17a5a33be55bd\" id=\"13bdfaab508140529218500d5f009322\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52961\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8e7c90e21df1457898ae7d4dc6cd2f44\" title=\"FSCS\">FSCS</a></em> may reduce, remit or refund any overpaid amounts paid in respect of a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> in respect of a particular period, due to a mistake of law or fact by a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> or, where applicable, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>, provided that the claim is made by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> or, where applicable, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em> not more than two years after the beginning of the period to which the overpayment relates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/12-10-2016#13bdfaab508140529218500d5f009322\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.4 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"3a0cad050714426eaea0bb29cb719417\" id=\"a6a7c30eddff4fc5a867506f427bcadf\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.5\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>If a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> (and, where applicable, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>), does not pay the total amount of its share of a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em>, before the end of the date on which it is due, it must pay an additional amount as follows:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) if the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> was not paid in full before the end of the due date, an administrative fee of £250; and</li>\n<li>(2) interest on any unpaid part of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53190\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7a5accf3c10f48eea12c51f0ad083d84\" title=\"MERS levy\">MERS levy</a></em> or administrative fee at the rate of 5% per annum above the Official Bank Rate from time to time in force, accruing on a daily basis from the date on which the amount concerned became due.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/management-expenses-in-respect-of-relevant-schemes/03-07-2015#a6a7c30eddff4fc5a867506f427bcadf\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.5 before 30/11/2022\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>",
